<center><font face="Times_CSX+"><font size=+3>Suttantapi&ntilde;ake - khuddakanik&agrave;ye</font></font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+"><font size=+2>Cullaniddesap&agrave;&euml;i</font></font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Namo tassa bhagavato arahato samm&agrave;sambuddhassa</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+"><font size=+2>P&agrave;r&agrave;yana vaggo</font></font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+"><font size=+2>6. Upas&atilde;va suttaniddeso</font></font></center>
<font face="Times_CSX+">6-1</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Eko aha&uuml; sakka, mahantamogha&uuml; (icc&agrave;yasm&agrave;
upas&atilde;vo)</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Anissito no visah&agrave;mi t&agrave;ritu&uuml;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">&acirc;ramma&otilde;a&uuml; br&aring;hi samantacakkhu</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Ya&uuml; nissito oghamima&uuml; tareyya&uuml;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Eko aha&uuml; sakka mahantamoghanti 'eko'ti
puggalo v&agrave; me dutiyo natthi, dhammo v&agrave; me dutiyo natthi,
ya&uuml; v&agrave; puggala&uuml; niss&agrave;ya, dhamma&uuml; v&agrave;
niss&agrave;ya mahanta&uuml; k&agrave;mogha&uuml; bhavogha&uuml; di&ntilde;&ntilde;hogha&uuml;
avijjogha&uuml; tareyya&uuml; uttareyya&uuml; patareyya&uuml; samatikkameyya&uuml;
v&atilde;tivatteyyanti eko. Sakk&agrave;ti sakko, bhagav&agrave; 'sakyakul&agrave;
pabbajitoti'pi sakko. Athav&agrave; 'a&oacute;&oacute;ho mahaddhano dhanav&agrave;ti'pi
sakko. Tassim&agrave;ni dhan&agrave;ni, seyyath&atilde;da&uuml;: saddh&agrave;dhana&uuml;
s&atilde;ladhana&uuml; hiridhana&uuml; ottappadhana&uuml; sutadhana&uuml;
c&agrave;gadhana&uuml; pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;dhana&uuml; satipa&ntilde;&ntilde;h&agrave;nadhana&uuml;
sammappadh&agrave;nadhana&uuml; iddhip&agrave;dadhana&uuml; indriyadhana&uuml;
baladhana&uuml; bojjha&iuml;gadhana&uuml; maggadhana&uuml; phaladhana&uuml;
nibb&agrave;nadhana&uuml;, imebhi anekehi dhanaratanehi1 a&oacute;&oacute;ho
mahaddhano dhanav&agrave;ti'pi sakko. Athav&agrave; sakko pahu visav&atilde;
alamatto2 s&aring;ro v&atilde;ro3 vikkanto abh&atilde;ru acchambhi anutr&agrave;si
apal&agrave;y&atilde; pah&atilde;nabhayabheravo vigatalomaha&uuml;so'tipi
sakkoti 'eko aha&uuml; sakka mahantamogha&uuml;'.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Icc&agrave;yasm&agrave; upas&atilde;voti 'icc&agrave;'ti
padasandhi padasa&uuml;saggo padap&agrave;rip&aring;ri akkharasamav&agrave;yo
bya&curren;janasili&ntilde;&ntilde;hat&agrave; pad&agrave;nupubbat&agrave;peta&uuml;
'icc&agrave;ti'. &acirc;yasm&agrave;'ti: piyavacana&uuml; garuvacana&uuml;
sag&agrave;ravasappatiss&agrave;dhivacanameta&uuml;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">'&acirc;yasm&agrave;'ti. Piyavacana&uuml;:
upas&atilde;voti tassa br&agrave;hma&otilde;assa n&agrave;ma&uuml; sa&iuml;kh&agrave;
sama&curren;&curren;&agrave; pa&curren;&curren;atti voh&agrave;ro n&agrave;ma&uuml;
n&agrave;makamma&uuml; n&agrave;madheyya&uuml; niruttibya&curren;jana&uuml;
abhil&agrave;poti 'icc&agrave;yasm&agrave; upas&atilde;vo'.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Anissito no visah&agrave;mi t&agrave;ritunti
anissito'ti puggala&uuml; v&agrave; anissito, dhamma&uuml; v&agrave; anissito,
no visah&agrave;mi, na ussah&agrave;mi, na sakkomi, na pa&ntilde;ibalo,
mahanta&uuml; k&agrave;mogha&uuml; bhavogha&uuml; di&ntilde;&ntilde;hogha&uuml;
avijjogha&uuml; taritu&uuml; uttaritu&uuml; pataritu&uuml; samatikkamitu&uuml;
v&atilde;tivattitunti 'anissito no visah&agrave;mi t&agrave;ritu&uuml;'.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">1. Dhammaratanehi-va, vi</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">2. Pahu vibhav&atilde; alamatto-va, v&atilde;,
ka</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">3. Dh&atilde;ro-va, vi</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">[BJT Page 222] [\x 222/]</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">&acirc;ramma&otilde;a&uuml; br&aring;hi samantacakkh&aring;ti
'&agrave;ramma&otilde;a'nti &agrave;lambana&uuml;1 nissaya&uuml; upanissaya&uuml;.
Br&aring;h&atilde;ti &agrave;cikkh&agrave;hi desehi pa&curren;&curren;apehi
pa&ntilde;&ntilde;hapehi vivar&agrave;hi vibhaj&agrave;hi utt&agrave;n&atilde;karohi
pak&agrave;sehi. Samantacakkh&aring;hi 'samantacakkhu' vuccati sabba&curren;&curren;uta&curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml;,
bhagav&agrave; tena sabba&curren;&curren;uta&curren;&agrave;&otilde;ena
upeto samupeto upagato samupagato uppanno2 sampanno3 samann&agrave;gato.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">''Na tassa addi&ntilde;&ntilde;hamidhatthi ki&curren;ci</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Ato avi&curren;&curren;&agrave;tamaj&agrave;nitabba&uuml;,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Sabba&uuml; abhi&curren;&curren;&agrave;si
yadatthi neyya&uuml;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Tath&agrave;gato tena samantacakkh&aring;''ti.
[A]</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">'&acirc;ramma&otilde;a&uuml; br&aring;hi samantacakkhu.
'</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Ya&uuml; nissito oghamima&uuml; tareyyanti 'ya&uuml;
nissito'ti ya&uuml; puggala&uuml; v&agrave; nissito, dhamma&uuml; v&agrave;
nissito, mahanta&uuml; k&agrave;mogha&uuml; bhavogha&uuml; di&ntilde;&ntilde;hogha&uuml;
avijjogha&uuml; tareyya&uuml; uttareyya&uuml; patareyya&uuml; samatikkameyya&uuml;
v&atilde;tivatteyyanti 'ya&uuml; nissito oghamima&uuml; tareyya&uuml;.
'</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Ten&agrave;ha so br&agrave;hma&otilde;o:</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">''Eko aha&uuml; sakka mahantamogha&uuml; (icc&agrave;yasm&agrave;
upas&atilde;vo)</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Anissito no visah&agrave;mi t&agrave;ritu&uuml;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">&acirc;ramma&otilde;a&uuml; br&aring;hi samantacakkhu</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Ya&uuml; nissito oghamima&uuml; tareyya''nti</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">6-2</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">&acirc;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;a&uuml; pekkham&agrave;no
sat&atilde;m&agrave; (upas&atilde;v&agrave;'ti bhagav&agrave;)</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Natth&atilde;ti niss&agrave;ya tarassu ogha&uuml;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">K&agrave;me pah&agrave;ya virato kath&agrave;hi</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Ta&otilde;hakkhaya&uuml; nattamah&agrave;bhipassa4.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">&acirc;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;a&uuml; pekkam&agrave;no
satim&agrave;ti so br&agrave;hma&otilde;o pakatiy&agrave; &agrave;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;&agrave;yatanasam&agrave;pattil&agrave;bh&atilde;
santa&uuml; yeva5 nissaya&uuml; na j&agrave;n&agrave;ti 'aya&uuml; me nissayo'ti
tassa bhagav&agrave; nissaya&uuml; ca &agrave;cikkhati, uttari&curren;ca
niyy&agrave;napatha&uuml;. &acirc;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;&agrave;yatanasam&agrave;patti&uuml;
sato sam&agrave;pajjitv&agrave; tato vu&ntilde;&ntilde;hahitv&agrave; tattha
j&agrave;te cittacetasike dhamme aniccato pekkham&agrave;no dukkhato -
rogato - ga&otilde;&oacute;ato - sallato - aghato - &agrave;b&agrave;dhato
- parato - palokato - &atilde;tito - uppaddavato - bhayato - upassaggato
- calato - pabha&iuml;guto - addhuvato - at&agrave;&otilde;ato - alenato
- asara&otilde;ato -</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">1. &acirc;ramma&otilde;a&uuml; &agrave;lamba&otilde;a&uuml;
- machasa&uuml;, sy&agrave;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">2. Uppanno - katthaci</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">3. Samupapanno - machasa&uuml;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">4. Rattamah&agrave;bhipassa - sy&agrave;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">5. Sam&agrave;pattil&agrave;bh&atilde;yeva
- machasa&uuml;, sy&agrave;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">[A.] Pa&ntilde;isambhid&agrave;magga - &curren;&agrave;&otilde;a
kath&agrave;, indriya kath&agrave;</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">[BJT Page 224] [\x 224/]</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Asara&otilde;&atilde;bh&aring;tato - rittato
- tucchato - su&curren;&curren;ato - anattato - &agrave;d&atilde;navato
- v&atilde;parin&agrave;madhammato - as&agrave;rakato - agham&aring;lato
vadhakato vibhavato' - s&agrave;savato - sa&iuml;khatato - m&agrave;r&agrave;misato
- j&agrave;tidhammato - jar&agrave;dhammato - vy&agrave;dhidhammato - mara&otilde;adhammato
- sokaparidevadukkhadomanassup&agrave;y&agrave;sadhammato - sa&uuml;kilesikadhammato
- samudayadhammato - attha&iuml;gamato - ass&agrave;dato - &agrave;d&atilde;navato
- nissara&otilde;ato - pekkham&agrave;no dakkham&agrave;no olokayam&agrave;no
nijjh&agrave;yam&agrave;no upaparikkham&agrave;no. Satim&agrave;ti ''y&agrave;
sati anussati pa&ntilde;issati sati sara&otilde;at&agrave; dh&agrave;ra&otilde;at&agrave;
apil&agrave;panat&agrave; asammussanat&agrave; sati satindriya&uuml; satibala&uuml;
samm&agrave;sati aya&uuml; vuccati sati' im&agrave;ya satiy&agrave; upeto
hoti samupeto upagato samupagato upapanno sampanno samann&agrave;gato,
so vuccati satim&agrave;ti '&agrave;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;a&uuml;
pekkham&agrave;no sat&atilde;m&agrave;. '</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Upas&atilde;v&agrave;ti bhagav&agrave;ti 'upas&atilde;v&agrave;'ti
bhagav&agrave; ta&uuml; br&agrave;hma&otilde;a&uuml; n&agrave;mena &agrave;lapati,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Bhagav&agrave;ti g&agrave;rav&agrave;dhivacanameta&uuml;:</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Apica, bhaggar&agrave;goti bhagav&agrave;:
bhaggadosoti bhagav&agrave;: bhaggamohoti bhagav&agrave;: bhaggam&agrave;noti
bhagav&agrave;: bhaggadi&ntilde;&ntilde;h&atilde;ti bhagav&agrave;: bhaggaka&otilde;&ntilde;akoti
bhagav&agrave;: bhaggakilesoti bhagav&agrave;: bhaji vibhaji pavibhaji
dhammaratananti bhagav&agrave;: bhav&agrave;na&uuml; antakaroti bhagav&agrave;
: bh&agrave;vitak&agrave;yo bh&agrave;vitas&atilde;lo bh&agrave;vitacitto
bh&agrave;vitapa&curren;&curren;oti bhagav&agrave;: bhaji v&agrave; bhagav&agrave;
ara&curren;&curren;e vanapatth&agrave;ni pant&agrave;ni sen&agrave;san&agrave;ni
appasadd&agrave;ni appanigghos&agrave;ni vijanav&agrave;t&agrave;ni manussar&agrave;haseyyak&agrave;ni
pa&ntilde;isall&agrave;nas&agrave;rupp&agrave;n&atilde;ti bhagav&agrave;:
bh&agrave;g&atilde; v&agrave; bhagav&agrave; c&atilde;varapi&otilde;&oacute;ap&agrave;tasen&agrave;sanagil&agrave;napaccayabhesajjaparikkh&agrave;r&agrave;nanti
bhagav&agrave;: bh&agrave;g&atilde; v&agrave; bhagav&agrave; attharasassa
dhammarasassa vimuttirasassa adhis&atilde;lassa adhicittassa adhipa&curren;&curren;&agrave;y&agrave;ti
bhagav&agrave;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Bh&agrave;g&atilde; v&agrave; bhagav&agrave;
catunna&uuml; jh&agrave;n&agrave;na&uuml; catunna&uuml; appama&curren;&curren;&agrave;na&uuml;
catunna&uuml; ar&aring;pasam&agrave;patt&atilde;nanti bhagav&agrave;, bh&agrave;g&atilde;
v&agrave; bhagav&agrave; a&ntilde;&ntilde;hanna&uuml; vimokkh&agrave;na&uuml;
a&ntilde;&ntilde;hanna&uuml; abhibh&agrave;yatan&agrave;na&uuml; navanna&uuml;
anupubbavih&agrave;rasam&agrave;patt&atilde;nanti bhagav&agrave;: bh&agrave;g&atilde;
v&agrave; bhagav&agrave; dasanna&uuml; sa&curren;&curren;&agrave;bh&agrave;van&agrave;na&uuml;
dasanna&uuml; kasi&otilde;asam&agrave;patt&atilde;na&uuml;, &agrave;n&agrave;p&agrave;nasatisam&agrave;dhissa
asubhasam&agrave;pattiy&agrave;ti bhagav&agrave;, bh&agrave;g&atilde; v&agrave;
bhagav&agrave; catunna&uuml; satipa&ntilde;&ntilde;h&agrave;n&agrave;na&uuml;
catunna&uuml; sammappadh&agrave;n&agrave;na&uuml; catunna&uuml; iddhip&agrave;d&agrave;na&uuml;
pa&curren;canna&uuml; indriy&agrave;na&uuml; pa&curren;canna&uuml; bal&agrave;na&uuml;
sattanna&uuml; bojjha&iuml;g&agrave;na&uuml; ariyassa a&ntilde;&ntilde;ha&iuml;gikassa
maggass&agrave;ti bhagav&agrave;: bh&agrave;g&atilde; v&agrave; bhagav&agrave;
dasanna&uuml; tath&agrave;gatabal&agrave;na&uuml; catunna&uuml; ves&agrave;rajj&agrave;na&uuml;
catunna&uuml; pa&ntilde;isambhid&agrave;na&uuml; channa&uuml; abhi&curren;&curren;&agrave;na&uuml;
channa&uuml; buddhadhamm&agrave;nanti bhagav&agrave;: bhagav&agrave;ti
neta&uuml; n&agrave;ma&uuml; m&agrave;tar&agrave; kata&uuml;, na pitar&agrave;
kata&uuml;, na bh&agrave;tar&agrave; kata&uuml;, na bhaginiy&agrave; kata&uuml;,
na mitt&agrave;maccehi kata&uuml;, na &curren;&agrave;tis&agrave;lohitehi
kata&uuml;, na sama&otilde;abr&agrave;hma&otilde;ehi kata&uuml;, na devat&agrave;hi
kata&uuml;, vimokkhantikameta&uuml; buddh&agrave;na&uuml; bhagavant&agrave;na&uuml;
bodhiy&agrave; m&aring;le saha sabba&curren;&curren;uta&curren;&agrave;&otilde;assa
pa&ntilde;il&agrave;bh&agrave; sacchik&agrave; pa&curren;&curren;atti yadida&uuml;
bhagav&agrave;ti 'upas&atilde;v&agrave;ti bhagav&agrave;. '</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Natth&atilde;ti niss&agrave;ya tarassu oghanti
'natthi ki&curren;c&atilde;'ti &agrave;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;&agrave;yatanasam&agrave;patti'
ki&uuml;k&agrave;ra&otilde;&agrave; 'natthi ki&curren;c&atilde;'ti &agrave;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;&agrave;yatanasam&agrave;patti
vi&curren;&curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&curren;c&agrave;yatanasam&agrave;patti
sato sam&agrave;pajjitv&agrave; tato vu&ntilde;&ntilde;hahitv&agrave; ta&curren;&curren;eva
vi&curren;&curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml; abh&agrave;veti vyabh&agrave;veti2
antaradh&agrave;peti3 'natthi ki&curren;c&atilde;'ti passati, ta&uuml;k&agrave;ra&otilde;&agrave;
'natthi ki&curren;c&atilde;'ti &agrave;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;&agrave;yatanasam&agrave;patti,
ta&uuml; niss&agrave;ya3 upaniss&agrave;ya &agrave;lambana&uuml;4 karitv&agrave;
k&agrave;mogha&uuml; bhavogha&uuml; di&ntilde;&ntilde;hogha&uuml; avijjogha&uuml;
tarassu uttarassu patarassu samatikkamassu v&atilde;tivattass&aring;t&atilde;
'natth&atilde;ti niss&agrave;ya tarassu ogha&uuml;'.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">K&agrave;me pah&agrave;ya virato kath&agrave;h&atilde;ti
'k&agrave;m&agrave;'ti udd&agrave;nato dve k&agrave;m&agrave;: vatthuk&agrave;m&agrave;
ca kilesak&agrave;m&agrave; ca.</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Katame vatthuk&agrave;m&agrave;? Man&agrave;pik&agrave;
r&aring;p&agrave; man&agrave;pik&agrave; sadd&agrave; man&agrave;pik&agrave;
gandh&agrave; man&agrave;pik&agrave; ras&agrave; man&agrave;pik&agrave;
pho&ntilde;&ntilde;habb&agrave;, atthara&otilde;&agrave; p&agrave;pura&otilde;&agrave;,
d&agrave;sid&agrave;s&agrave; aje&euml;ak&agrave; kukku&ntilde;as&aring;kar&agrave;
hatthigav&agrave;ssava&euml;av&agrave;, khetta&uuml; vatthu hira&curren;&curren;a&uuml;
suva&otilde;&otilde;a&uuml; g&agrave;manigamar&agrave;jadh&agrave;niyo
ra&ntilde;&ntilde;ha&uuml; ca janapado ca koso ca ko&ntilde;&ntilde;h&agrave;g&agrave;ra&uuml;
ca, ya&uuml; ki&curren;ci rajan&atilde;ya&uuml; vatthu vatthuk&agrave;m&agrave;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Api ca, at&atilde;t&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;,
an&agrave;gat&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;, paccuppann&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;,
ajjhatt&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;, bahiddh&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;,
ajjhattabahiddh&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;, h&atilde;n&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;,
majjhim&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;, pa&otilde;&atilde;t&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;,
&agrave;p&agrave;yik&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;, m&agrave;nusik&agrave;
k&agrave;m&agrave;, dibb&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;, paccupa&ntilde;&ntilde;hit&agrave;
k&agrave;m&agrave;, nimmit&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;, parinimmit&agrave;
k&agrave;m&agrave;, animmit&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;, pariggahit&agrave;
k&agrave;m&agrave;, apariggahit&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;, mam&agrave;yit&agrave;
k&agrave;m&agrave;, amam&agrave;yit&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;, sabbe'pi
k&agrave;m&agrave;vacar&agrave; dhamm&agrave;, sabbe'pi r&aring;p&agrave;vacar&agrave;
dhamm&agrave;, sabbe'pi ar&aring;p&agrave;vacar&agrave; dhamm&agrave;,
ta&otilde;h&agrave;vatthuk&agrave; ta&otilde;h&agrave;ramma&otilde;&agrave;
kaman&atilde;ya&ntilde;&ntilde;hena rajan&atilde;ya&ntilde;&ntilde;hena
madan&atilde;ya&ntilde;&ntilde;hena k&agrave;m&agrave;. Ime vuccanti vatthuk&agrave;m&agrave;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Katame kilesak&agrave;m&agrave;? Chando k&agrave;mo,
r&agrave;go k&agrave;mo, chandar&agrave;go k&agrave;mo: sa&iuml;kappo k&agrave;mo,
r&agrave;go k&agrave;mo, sa&iuml;kappar&agrave;go k&agrave;mo: yo k&agrave;mesu
k&agrave;macchando, k&agrave;mar&agrave;go, k&agrave;manandi, k&agrave;mata&otilde;h&agrave;,
k&agrave;masineho, k&agrave;mapari&euml;&agrave;ho, k&agrave;mamucch&agrave;,
k&agrave;majjhos&agrave;na&uuml;, k&agrave;mogho, k&agrave;mayogo, k&agrave;m&aring;p&agrave;d&agrave;na&uuml;,
k&agrave;macchandan&atilde;vara&otilde;a&uuml;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">''Addasa&uuml; k&agrave;ma&uuml; te m&aring;la&uuml;
sa&iuml;kapp&agrave; k&agrave;ma j&agrave;yasi,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Na ta&uuml; sa&iuml;kappayiss&agrave;mi eva&uuml;
k&agrave;me na hehis&atilde;''ti</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Ime vuccanti kilesak&agrave;m&agrave;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">[BJT Page 224] [\x 224/]</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">K&agrave;me pah&agrave;y&agrave;ti vatthuk&agrave;me
parij&agrave;nitv&agrave; kilesak&agrave;me pah&agrave;ya pajahitv&agrave;
vinodetv&agrave; byant&atilde;karitv&agrave; anabh&agrave;va&uuml; gametv&agrave;ti
k&agrave;me pah&agrave;ya pajahitv&agrave; vinodetv&agrave; byant&atilde;karitv&agrave;
anabh&agrave;va&uuml; gametv&agrave;ti 'k&agrave;me pah&agrave;ya'. Virato
kath&agrave;h&atilde;ti 'katha&uuml;kath&agrave;' vuccati vicikicch&agrave;,
dukkhe ka&iuml;kh&agrave;, dukkhasamudaye ka&iuml;kh&agrave;, dukkhanirodhe
ka&iuml;kh&agrave;,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Dukkhanirodhag&agrave;miniy&agrave; pa&ntilde;ipad&agrave;ya
ka&iuml;kh&agrave;, pubbante ka&iuml;kh&agrave; , aparante ka&iuml;kh&agrave;,
pubbant&agrave;parante ka&iuml;kh&agrave;, idappaccayat&agrave;pa&ntilde;iccasamuppannesu
dhammesu ka&iuml;kh&agrave;. Y&agrave; evar&aring;p&agrave; ka&iuml;kh&agrave;
ka&iuml;kh&agrave;yan&agrave; ka&iuml;kh&agrave;yitatta&uuml; vimati vicikicch&agrave;
dve&euml;haka&uuml; dvedh&agrave;patho sa&uuml;sayo aneka&uuml;sag&agrave;ho
&agrave;sappan&agrave; parisappan&agrave; apariyog&agrave;han&agrave; thambhitatta&uuml;6
cittassa manovilekho. ' Katha&uuml;kath&agrave;ya &agrave;rato virato pa&ntilde;ivirato
nikkhanto nissa&ntilde;o vippayutto7 visa&uuml;yutto vimariy&agrave;d&atilde;katena
cetas&agrave; viharat&atilde;ti evampi 'virato kath&agrave;hi'. Athav&agrave;
dvatti&uuml;s&agrave;ya tiracch&agrave;nakath&agrave;ya &agrave;rato virato
pa&ntilde;ivirato nikkhanto nissa&ntilde;o vippayutto7 visa&uuml;yutto
vimariy&agrave;d&atilde;katena cetas&agrave; viharat&atilde;ti evampi virato
kath&agrave;h&atilde;ti 'k&agrave;me pah&agrave;ya virato kath&agrave;hi.
'</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">1. Bhavato vibhavato-va, vi</font>
