<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Ta&otilde;hakkhaya&uuml; nattamah&agrave;bhipass&agrave;ti
'ta&otilde;h&agrave;'ti r&aring;pata&otilde;h&agrave;, saddata&otilde;h&agrave;,
