<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Ten&agrave;ha bhagav&agrave;:</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">''&acirc;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;a&uuml;
pekkham&agrave;no sat&atilde;m&agrave; (upas&atilde;v&agrave;ti bhagav&agrave;)</font>
