<p><font face="Times_CSX+">6-3</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Sabbesu k&agrave;mesu yo v&atilde;tar&agrave;go
(icc&agrave;yasm&agrave; upas&atilde;vo)</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">&acirc;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;a&uuml;
nissayo hitva ma&curren;&curren;a&uuml;3</font>
