<br><font face="Times_CSX+">K&agrave;mes&aring;ti 'k&agrave;m&agrave;'ti:
udd&agrave;nato dve k&agrave;m&agrave; vatthuk&agrave;m&agrave; ca kilesak&agrave;m&agrave;
ca. Katame vatthuk&agrave;m&agrave;? Man&agrave;pik&agrave; r&aring;p&agrave;
man&agrave;pik&agrave; sadd&agrave; man&agrave;pik&agrave; gandh&agrave;
man&agrave;pik&agrave; ras&agrave; man&agrave;pik&agrave; pho&ntilde;&ntilde;habb&agrave;,
atthara&otilde;&agrave; p&agrave;pura&otilde;&agrave;, d&agrave;sid&agrave;s&agrave;
aje&euml;ak&agrave; kukku&ntilde;as&aring;kar&agrave; hatthigav&agrave;ssava&euml;av&agrave;,
khetta&uuml; vatthu hira&curren;&curren;a&uuml; suva&otilde;&otilde;a&uuml;
g&agrave;manigamar&agrave;jadh&agrave;niyo ra&ntilde;&ntilde;ha&uuml; ca
janapado ca koso ca ko&ntilde;&ntilde;h&agrave;g&agrave;ra&uuml; ca, ya&uuml;
ki&curren;ci rajan&atilde;ya&uuml; vatthu vatthuk&agrave;m&agrave;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Api ca, at&atilde;t&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;,
an&agrave;gat&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;, paccuppann&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;,
ajjhatt&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;, bahiddh&agrave; k&agrave;m&agrave;,
