t&agrave;sa&uuml;1 &agrave;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;&agrave;yatanasam&agrave;patti
vimokkho aggo ca se&ntilde;&ntilde;ho ca vise&ntilde;&ntilde;ho ca p&agrave;mokkho
