<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Ti&ntilde;&ntilde;he nu so tattha an&agrave;nuy&agrave;y&atilde;ti
'ti&ntilde;&ntilde;he n&aring;'ti sa&uuml;sayapucch&agrave; vimatipucch&agrave;
dve&euml;hakapucch&agrave; aneka&uuml;sapucch&agrave; 'eva&uuml; nu kho
