<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Katame kilesak&agrave;m&agrave;? Chando k&agrave;mo,
r&agrave;go k&agrave;mo, chandar&agrave;go k&agrave;mo: sa&iuml;kappo k&agrave;mo,
r&agrave;go k&agrave;mo, sa&iuml;kappar&agrave;go k&agrave;mo: yo k&agrave;mesu
k&agrave;macchando, k&agrave;mar&agrave;go, k&agrave;manandi, k&agrave;mata&otilde;h&agrave;,
k&agrave;masineho, k&agrave;mapari&euml;&agrave;ho, k&agrave;mamucch&agrave;,
k&agrave;majjhos&agrave;na&uuml;, k&agrave;mogho, k&agrave;mayogo, k&agrave;m&aring;p&agrave;d&agrave;na&uuml;,
k&agrave;macchandan&atilde;vara&otilde;a&uuml;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">''Addasa&uuml; k&agrave;ma&uuml; te m&aring;la&uuml;
sa&iuml;kapp&agrave; k&agrave;ma j&agrave;yasi,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Na ta&uuml; sa&iuml;kappayiss&agrave;mi eva&uuml;
k&agrave;me na hehis&atilde;''ti</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Ime vuccanti kilesak&agrave;m&agrave;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Sabbesu k&agrave;mesu yo v&atilde;tar&agrave;goti
sabbesu k&agrave;mesu yo v&atilde;tar&agrave;go vigatar&agrave;go cattar&agrave;go
vantar&agrave;go muttar&agrave;go pah&atilde;nar&agrave;go pa&ntilde;inissa&ntilde;&ntilde;har&agrave;go
vikkhambhanatoti 'sabbesu k&agrave;mesu yo v&atilde;tar&agrave;go. '</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">1. Sa&curren;&curren;&agrave;sam&agrave;patt&atilde;na&uuml;-machasa&uuml;,
sy&agrave;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">2. An&agrave;nuv&agrave;yi-katthaci</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">3. Adheva m&agrave;no-sy&agrave;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">4. Paramevimutto-va, vi</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">[BJT Page 230] [\x 230/]</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Upas&atilde;v&agrave;ti bhagav&agrave;ti 'upas&atilde;v&agrave;'ti
bhagav&agrave; ta&uuml; br&agrave;hma&otilde;a&uuml; n&agrave;mena &agrave;lapati,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Bhagav&agrave;ti g&agrave;rav&agrave;dhivacanameta&uuml;:</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Apica, bhaggar&agrave;goti bhagav&agrave;:
bhaggadosoti bhagav&agrave;: bhaggamohoti bhagav&agrave;: bhaggam&agrave;noti
bhagav&agrave;: bhaggadi&ntilde;&ntilde;h&atilde;ti bhagav&agrave;: bhaggaka&otilde;&ntilde;akoti
bhagav&agrave;: bhaggakilesoti bhagav&agrave;: bhaji vibhaji pavibhaji
dhammaratananti bhagav&agrave;: bhav&agrave;na&uuml; antakaroti bhagav&agrave;
: bh&agrave;vitak&agrave;yo bh&agrave;vitas&atilde;lo bh&agrave;vitacitto
bh&agrave;vitapa&curren;&curren;oti bhagav&agrave;: bhaji v&agrave; bhagav&agrave;
ara&curren;&curren;e vanapatth&agrave;ni pant&agrave;ni sen&agrave;san&agrave;ni
appasadd&agrave;ni appanigghos&agrave;ni vijanav&agrave;t&agrave;ni manussar&agrave;haseyyak&agrave;ni
pa&ntilde;isall&agrave;nas&agrave;rupp&agrave;n&atilde;ti bhagav&agrave;:
bh&agrave;g&atilde; v&agrave; bhagav&agrave; c&atilde;varapi&otilde;&oacute;ap&agrave;tasen&agrave;sanagil&agrave;napaccayabhesajjaparikkh&agrave;r&agrave;nanti
bhagav&agrave;: bh&agrave;g&atilde; v&agrave; bhagav&agrave; attharasassa
dhammarasassa vimuttirasassa adhis&atilde;lassa adhicittassa adhipa&curren;&curren;&agrave;y&agrave;ti
bhagav&agrave;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Bh&agrave;g&atilde; v&agrave; bhagav&agrave;
catunna&uuml; jh&agrave;n&agrave;na&uuml; catunna&uuml; appama&curren;&curren;&agrave;na&uuml;
catunna&uuml; ar&aring;pasam&agrave;patt&atilde;nanti bhagav&agrave;, bh&agrave;g&atilde;
v&agrave; bhagav&agrave; a&ntilde;&ntilde;hanna&uuml; vimokkh&agrave;na&uuml;
a&ntilde;&ntilde;hanna&uuml; abhibh&agrave;yatan&agrave;na&uuml; navanna&uuml;
anupubbavih&agrave;rasam&agrave;patt&atilde;nanti bhagav&agrave;: bh&agrave;g&atilde;
v&agrave; bhagav&agrave; dasanna&uuml; sa&curren;&curren;&agrave;bh&agrave;van&agrave;na&uuml;
dasanna&uuml; kasi&otilde;asam&agrave;patt&atilde;na&uuml;, &agrave;n&agrave;p&agrave;nasatisam&agrave;dhissa
asubhasam&agrave;pattiy&agrave;ti bhagav&agrave;, bh&agrave;g&atilde; v&agrave;
bhagav&agrave; catunna&uuml; satipa&ntilde;&ntilde;h&agrave;n&agrave;na&uuml;
catunna&uuml; sammappadh&agrave;n&agrave;na&uuml; catunna&uuml; iddhip&agrave;d&agrave;na&uuml;
pa&curren;canna&uuml; indriy&agrave;na&uuml; pa&curren;canna&uuml; bal&agrave;na&uuml;
sattanna&uuml; bojjha&iuml;g&agrave;na&uuml; ariyassa a&ntilde;&ntilde;ha&iuml;gikassa
maggass&agrave;ti bhagav&agrave;: bh&agrave;g&atilde; v&agrave; bhagav&agrave;
dasanna&uuml; tath&agrave;gatabal&agrave;na&uuml; catunna&uuml; ves&agrave;rajj&agrave;na&uuml;
catunna&uuml; pa&ntilde;isambhid&agrave;na&uuml; channa&uuml; abhi&curren;&curren;&agrave;na&uuml;
channa&uuml; buddhadhamm&agrave;nanti bhagav&agrave;: bhagav&agrave;ti
neta&uuml; n&agrave;ma&uuml; m&agrave;tar&agrave; kata&uuml;, na pitar&agrave;
kata&uuml;, na bh&agrave;tar&agrave; kata&uuml;, na bhaginiy&agrave; kata&uuml;,
na mitt&agrave;maccehi kata&uuml;, na &curren;&agrave;tis&agrave;lohitehi
kata&uuml;, na sama&otilde;abr&agrave;hma&otilde;ehi kata&uuml;, na devat&agrave;hi
kata&uuml;, vimokkhantikameta&uuml; buddh&agrave;na&uuml; bhagavant&agrave;na&uuml;
bodhiy&agrave; m&aring;le saha sabba&curren;&curren;uta&curren;&agrave;&otilde;assa
pa&ntilde;il&agrave;bh&agrave; sacchik&agrave; pa&curren;&curren;atti yadida&uuml;
bhagav&agrave;ti 'upas&atilde;v&agrave;ti bhagav&agrave;. '</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">&acirc;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;a&uuml; nissayo
hitvama&curren;&curren;anti he&ntilde;&ntilde;him&agrave; cha sam&agrave;pattiyo
hitv&agrave; cajitv&agrave; pariccajitv&agrave; atikkamitv&agrave; samatikkamitv&agrave;
v&atilde;tivattitv&agrave; &agrave;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;&agrave;yatanasam&agrave;patti&uuml;
nissito assito all&atilde;no upagato samupagato ajjhosito adhimuttoti '&agrave;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;a&uuml;
nissito hitvama&curren;&curren;a&uuml;'</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Sa&curren;&curren;&agrave;vimokkhe paramedhimuttoti
'sa&curren;&curren;&agrave;vimokkh&agrave;' vuccanti sattasa&curren;&curren;&agrave;sam&agrave;pattiyo,
y&agrave;vat&agrave; sa&curren;&curren;&agrave;sam&agrave;patt&atilde;
t&agrave;sa&uuml; &agrave;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;&agrave;yatanasam&agrave;pattivimokkho
aggo ca se&ntilde;&ntilde;ho ca vise&ntilde;&ntilde;ho ca p&agrave;mokkho
ca uttamo ca pavaro ca, parame agge se&ntilde;&ntilde;he vise&ntilde;&ntilde;he
p&agrave;mokkhe uttame pavare adhimuttivimokkhen&agrave;dhimutto tatr&agrave;dhimutto
taccarito tabbahulo taggaruko tantinno tappo&otilde;o tappabh&agrave;ro
tadadhimutto tadadhipateyyoti 'sa&curren;&curren;&agrave;vimokkhe paramedhimutto.
'</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Ti&ntilde;&ntilde;heyya so tattha an&agrave;nuy&agrave;y&atilde;ti
'ti&ntilde;&ntilde;heyy&agrave;'ti ti&ntilde;&ntilde;heyya sa&ntilde;&ntilde;hikappasahass&agrave;ni,
tatth&agrave;ti &agrave;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;&agrave;yatane. An&agrave;nuy&agrave;y&atilde;ti
an&agrave;nuy&agrave;y&atilde; aviccam&agrave;no avigaccham&agrave;no1
anantaradh&agrave;yam&agrave;no aparih&agrave;yam&agrave;no, athav&agrave;
arajjam&agrave;no adussam&agrave;no amuyham&agrave;no akilissam&agrave;noti
'ti&ntilde;&ntilde;heyya so tattha an&agrave;nuy&agrave;y&atilde;. '</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Ten&agrave;ha bhagav&agrave;:</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">''Sabbesu k&agrave;mesu yo v&atilde;tar&agrave;go
(upas&atilde;v&agrave;ti bhagav&agrave;)</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">&acirc;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;a&uuml;
nissito hitvama&curren;&curren;a&uuml;,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Sa&curren;&curren;&agrave;vimokkhe paramedhimutto</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Ti&ntilde;&ntilde;heyya so tattha an&agrave;nuy&agrave;y&atilde;''ti.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">1. Adhigaccham&agrave;no-va, vi</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">[BJT Page 232] [\x 232/]</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">6-5</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Ti&ntilde;&ntilde;he ce so tattha an&agrave;nuy&agrave;yi</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">P&aring;gampi vass&agrave;na&uuml;1 samantacakkhu,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Tattheva so s&atilde;tisiy&agrave;2 vimutto</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Cavetha3 vi&curren;&curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml;
tath&agrave;vidhassa,</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Ti&ntilde;&ntilde;he ce so tattha an&agrave;nuy&agrave;y&atilde;ti
sace so ti&ntilde;&ntilde;heyya sa&ntilde;&ntilde;hikappasahass&agrave;ni:
tatth&agrave;ti &agrave;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;&agrave;yatane. An&agrave;nuy&agrave;y&atilde;ti
an&agrave;nuy&agrave;y&atilde; aviccam&agrave;no avigaccham&agrave;no anantaradh&agrave;nam&agrave;no
aparih&agrave;yam&agrave;no. Athav&agrave; arajjam&agrave;no adussam&agrave;no
amuyham&agrave;no akilissam&agrave;noti 'ti&ntilde;&ntilde;he ce so tattha
an&agrave;nuy&agrave;y&atilde;. '</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">P&aring;gampi vass&agrave;na&uuml; samantacakkh&aring;ti
'p&aring;gampi vass&agrave;na'nti p&aring;gampi vass&agrave;na&uuml; bah&aring;ni
vass&agrave;ni bah&aring;ni vassasat&agrave;ni bah&aring;ni vassasahass&agrave;ni
bah&aring;ni vassasatasahass&agrave;ni bah&aring;ni kapp&agrave;ni bah&aring;ni
kappasat&agrave;ni bah&aring;ni kappasahass&agrave;ni bah&aring;ni kappasatasahass&agrave;ni.
Samantacakkh&aring;ti 'samantacakkhu' vuccati sabba&curren;&curren;uta&curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml;,
bhagav&agrave; tena sabba&curren;&curren;uta&curren;&agrave;&otilde;ena
upeto samupeto upagato samupagato uppanno sampanno samann&agrave;gato</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">''Na tassa adi&ntilde;&ntilde;hamidhatthi ki&curren;ci</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Ato avi&curren;&curren;&agrave;tamaj&agrave;nitabba&uuml;,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Sabba&uuml; abhi&curren;&curren;&agrave;si
yadatthi neyya&uuml;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Tath&agrave;gato tena samantacakkh&aring;''ti</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">'P&aring;gampi vass&agrave;na&uuml;1 samantacakkhu'</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Tattheva so s&atilde;tisiy&agrave; vimutto cavetha
vi&curren;&curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml; tath&agrave;vidhass&agrave;ti
tattheva so s&atilde;t&atilde;bh&agrave;vamanuppatto nicco dhuvo sassato
aviparin&agrave;madhammo sassatisama&uuml; tatheva ti&ntilde;&ntilde;heyya.
' Athav&agrave; tassa vi&curren;&curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml; caveyya
ucchijjeyya nasseyya vinasseyya na bhaveyya4 punabbhavapa&ntilde;isandhivi&curren;&curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml;
nibbatteyya k&agrave;madh&agrave;tuy&agrave; v&agrave; r&aring;padh&agrave;tuy&agrave;
v&agrave; ar&aring;padh&agrave;tuy&agrave; v&agrave;'ti &agrave;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;&agrave;yatana&uuml;
sam&agrave;pannassa5 sassata&curren;ca uccheda&curren;ca pucchati ud&agrave;hu
tattheva anup&agrave;dises&agrave;ya nibb&agrave;nadh&agrave;tuy&agrave;
parinibb&agrave;yeyya athav&agrave; tassa vi&curren;&curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml;
caveyya, puna pa&ntilde;isandhivi&curren;&curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml;
nibbatteyya k&agrave;madh&agrave;tuy&agrave; v&agrave; r&aring;padh&agrave;tuy&agrave;
v&agrave; ar&aring;padh&agrave;tuy&agrave; v&agrave;'ti &agrave;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;&agrave;yatana&uuml;
upapannassa parinibb&agrave;na&curren;ca pa&ntilde;isandhi&curren;ca pucchati6.
Tath&agrave;vidhass&agrave;ti tath&agrave;vidhassa t&agrave;disassa tassa&otilde;&ntilde;hitassa7
tappak&agrave;rassa tappa&ntilde;ibh&agrave;gassa8 &agrave;ki&curren;ca&curren;&curren;&agrave;yatana&uuml;
upapannass&agrave;ti tattheva so s&atilde;tisiy&agrave; vimutto cavetha
vi&curren;&curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml; tath&agrave;vidhassa'</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Ten&agrave;ha so br&agrave;hma&otilde;o:</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">''Ti&ntilde;&ntilde;he ve so tattha an&agrave;nuy&agrave;y&atilde;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">P&aring;gampi vass&agrave;na&uuml; samantacakkhu,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Tattheva so s&atilde;tisiy&agrave; vimutto</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Cavetha vi&curren;&curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml;
tath&agrave;vidhass&agrave;''ti.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">1. P&aring;gampi vass&agrave;ni-pa, va, v&atilde;,
machasa&uuml;, p&aring;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">2. Tattheva hos&atilde;ti-pana,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Tattheva s&agrave;p&atilde;tiy&agrave;-va,
vi</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">3. Bh&agrave;vetha-va, vi</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">4. Caveyya-pa, va, vi, ka</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Bhaveyy&agrave;ti-machasa&uuml;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">5. Upapannassa-pana</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">6. Vuccati-pana</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">7. Tassatthitassa-pana</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">8. Tappa&ntilde;ibh&agrave;nassa-pana</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
