<p><font face="Times_CSX+">6-6</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Acc&atilde; yath&agrave; v&agrave;tavegena khitt&agrave;
(upas&atilde;v&agrave;'ti bhagav&agrave;)</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Attha&uuml; paleti na upeti sa&iuml;kha&uuml;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Eva&uuml; mun&atilde; n&agrave;mak&agrave;y&agrave;
vimutto</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Attha&uuml; paleti na upeti sa&iuml;kha&uuml;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Acc&atilde; yath&agrave; v&agrave;tavegena khitt&agrave;ti
- 'acci' vuccati j&agrave;lasikh&agrave;. V&agrave;t&agrave;ti puratthim&agrave;
v&agrave;t&agrave;, pacchim&agrave; v&agrave;t&agrave;, uttar&agrave; v&agrave;t&agrave;,
dakkhi&otilde;&agrave; v&agrave;t&agrave;, saraj&agrave; v&agrave;t&agrave;,
araj&agrave; v&agrave;t&agrave;, 1 s&atilde;t&agrave; v&agrave;t&agrave;,
u&otilde;h&agrave; v&agrave;t&agrave;, paritt&agrave; v&agrave;t&agrave;,
adhimatt&agrave; v&agrave;t&agrave;, k&agrave;&euml;av&agrave;t&agrave;,
2 verambhav&agrave;t&agrave;, pakkhav&agrave;t&agrave;, supa&otilde;&otilde;av&agrave;t&agrave;,
t&agrave;lapa&otilde;&otilde;av&agrave;t&agrave;, vidh&aring;panav&agrave;t&agrave;,
v&agrave;tavegena khitt&agrave;ti v&agrave;tavegena khitt&agrave; ukkhitt&agrave;
nunn&agrave; panunn&agrave; khambhit&agrave; vikkhambhit&agrave;ti 'acci
yath&agrave; v&agrave;tavegena khitt&agrave;, 'upas&atilde;v&agrave;ti
bhagav&agrave;'.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Attha&uuml; paleti na upeti sa&iuml;khanti -
'attha&uuml; palet&atilde;'ti attha&uuml; paleti, attha&uuml; gameti, attha&uuml;
gacchati, nirujjhati, v&aring;pasamati, pa&ntilde;ippassambhati. Na upeti
sa&iuml;khanti sa&iuml;kha&uuml; na upeti, uddesa&uuml; na upeti, ga&otilde;ana&uuml;
na upeti, pa&otilde;&otilde;atti&uuml; na upeti, puratthima&uuml; v&agrave;
disa&uuml; gato, pacchima&uuml; v&agrave; disa&uuml; gato, uttara&uuml;
v&agrave; disa&uuml; gato, dakkhi&otilde;a&uuml; v&agrave; disa&uuml; gato,
uddha&uuml; v&agrave; gato, adho v&agrave; gato, tiriya&uuml; v&agrave;
gato, vidisa&uuml; v&agrave; gatoti so hetu natthi, paccayo natthi, k&agrave;ra&otilde;a&uuml;
natthi yena sa&iuml;kha&uuml; gaccheyy&agrave;ti attha&uuml; paleti na
upeti sa&iuml;kha&uuml;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">. 7Eva&uuml; mun&atilde; n&agrave;mak&agrave;y&agrave;
vimuttoti 'eva'nti opammasampa&ntilde;ip&agrave;dana&uuml;, mun&atilde;ti
'mona&uuml;' vuccati &curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml;, y&agrave; pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;
paj&agrave;nan&agrave; vicayo pavicayo dhammavicayo sallakkha&otilde;&agrave;
upalakkha&otilde;&agrave; paccupalakkha&otilde;&agrave; pa&otilde;&oacute;icca&uuml;
kosalla&uuml; nepu&curren;&curren;a&uuml; vebhavy&agrave; cint&agrave;
upaparikkh&agrave; bh&aring;ri medh&agrave; pari&otilde;&agrave;yik&agrave;
vipassan&agrave; sampaja&curren;&curren;a&uuml; patodo pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;
pa&curren;&curren;indriya&uuml; pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;bala&uuml; pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;sattha&uuml;
pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;p&agrave;s&agrave;do pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;&agrave;loko
pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;obh&agrave;so pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;pajjoto
pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;p&agrave;s&agrave;do pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;&agrave;loko
pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;obh&agrave;so pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;pajjoto
pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;ratana&uuml; amoho dhammavicayo samm&agrave;di&ntilde;&ntilde;hi,
tena &curren;&agrave;&otilde;ena samann&agrave;gato muni monappattoti.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">T&atilde;&otilde;i moneyy&agrave;ni: k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;
vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml; manomoneyya&uuml;. Katama&uuml; k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;?
Tividh&agrave;na&uuml; k&agrave;yaduccarit&agrave;na&uuml; pah&agrave;na&uuml;
k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;. Tividha&uuml; k&agrave;yasucarita&uuml; k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;,
k&agrave;y&agrave;ramma&otilde;e &curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml; k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;,
k&agrave;yapari&curren;&curren;&agrave; k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;, pari&curren;&curren;&agrave;sahagato
maggo k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;, k&agrave;ye chandar&agrave;gassa pah&agrave;na&uuml;
k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;, k&agrave;yasa&uuml;kh&agrave;r&agrave;nirodho
catutthajjh&agrave;nasam&agrave;patti k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;. Ida&uuml;
k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Katama&uuml; vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;? Catubbidh&agrave;na&uuml;
vac&atilde;duccarit&agrave;na&uuml; pah&agrave;na&uuml; vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;,
vac&atilde;sucarita&uuml; vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;, v&agrave;c&agrave;ramma&otilde;e
&curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml; vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;, v&agrave;c&agrave;pari&curren;&curren;&agrave;
vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;, pari&curren;&curren;&agrave;sahagato maggo vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;,
v&agrave;c&agrave;ya chandar&agrave;gassa pah&agrave;na&uuml; vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;.
Vac&atilde;sa&uuml;kh&agrave;ranirodho dutiyajjh&agrave;nasam&agrave;patti
vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;. Ida&uuml; vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Katama&uuml; manomoneyya&uuml;? Tividh&agrave;na&uuml;
manoduccarit&agrave;na&uuml; pah&agrave;na&uuml; manomoneyya&uuml;, tividha&uuml;
manosucarita&uuml; manomoneyya&uuml;, citt&agrave;ramma&otilde;e &curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml;
manomoneyya&uuml;, cittapari&curren;&curren;&agrave; manomoneyya&uuml;,
pari&curren;&curren;&agrave;sahagato maggo manomoneyya&uuml;, citte chandar&agrave;gassa
pah&agrave;na&uuml; manomoneyya&uuml;, cittasa&uuml;kh&agrave;ranirodho
sa&curren;&curren;&agrave;vedayitanirodhasam&agrave;patti manomoneyya&uuml;.
Ida&uuml; manomoneyya&uuml;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">1. ''K&agrave;yamuni&uuml; v&agrave;c&agrave;muni&uuml;
manomuniman&agrave;sava&uuml;,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Muni&uuml; moneyyasampanna&uuml; &agrave;hu
sabbappah&agrave;yina&uuml;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">2. K&agrave;yamuni&uuml; v&agrave;c&agrave;muni&uuml;
manomuniman&agrave;sava&uuml;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Muni&uuml; moneyyasampanna&uuml; &agrave;hu
ninh&agrave;tap&agrave;paka''nti.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Imehi t&atilde;hi moneyyehi dhammehi samann&agrave;gato
cha munino: ag&agrave;ramunino anag&agrave;ramunino sekhamunino asekhamunino
paccekamunino munimuninoti. Katame ag&agrave;ramunino? Ye te ag&agrave;rik&agrave;
di&ntilde;&ntilde;hapad&agrave; vi&curren;&curren;&agrave;tas&agrave;san&agrave;,
ime ag&agrave;ramunino. Katame anag&agrave;ramunino? Ye te pabbajit&agrave;
di&ntilde;&ntilde;hapad&agrave; vi&curren;&curren;&agrave;tas&agrave;san&agrave;,
ime anag&agrave;ramunino. Satta sekh&agrave; sekhamunino. Arahanto asekhamunino.
Paccekabuddh&agrave; paccekamunino. Munimunino vuccanti tath&agrave;gat&agrave;
arahanto samm&agrave;sambuddh&agrave;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">3. ''Na monena muni hoti m&aring;&euml;har&aring;po
aviddasu,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Yo ca tula&uuml;va paggayha varam&agrave;d&agrave;ya
pa&otilde;&oacute;ito.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">4. P&agrave;p&agrave;ni parivajjeti sa mun&atilde;
tena so mun&atilde;,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Yo mun&agrave;ti ubho loke mun&atilde; tena
pavuccat&atilde;. ''</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">5. ''Asata&curren;ca sata&curren;ca &curren;atv&agrave;
dhamma&uuml;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Ajjhatta&uuml; bahiddh&agrave; ca sabbaloke,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Devamanussehi p&aring;jito yo</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Sa&iuml;gaj&agrave;lamaticca so mun&atilde;.</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">. 7</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">N&agrave;mak&agrave;y&agrave; vimuttoti so
muni pakatiy&agrave; pubbeva r&aring;pak&agrave;y&agrave; vimutto, tada&iuml;gasamatikkam&agrave;
vikkhambhanappah&agrave;nena pah&atilde;no, tassa munino bhavanta&uuml;
&agrave;gamma catt&agrave;ro ariyamagg&agrave; pa&ntilde;iladdh&agrave;
honti, catunna&uuml; ariyamagg&agrave;na&uuml; pa&ntilde;iladdhatt&agrave;
n&agrave;mak&agrave;yo ca r&aring;pak&agrave;yo ca pari&curren;&curren;&agrave;t&agrave;
honti, n&agrave;mak&agrave;yassa ca r&aring;pak&agrave;yassa ca pari&curren;&curren;&agrave;tatt&agrave;
n&agrave;mak&agrave;y&agrave; ca r&aring;pak&agrave;y&agrave; ca mutto
vimutto suvimutto accanta&uuml; anup&agrave;d&agrave;vimokkhen&agrave;ti
'eva&uuml;, mun&atilde; n&agrave;m&agrave;k&agrave;y&agrave; vimutto. '</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">1. Asaraj&agrave;v&agrave;t&agrave;-pana</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">2. K&agrave;&euml;av&agrave;t&agrave;ti-pana-potthake
natthi</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">[BJT Page 236] [\x 236/]</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Attha&uuml; paleti na upeti sa&iuml;khanti 'attha&uuml;
palet&atilde;'ti: an&agrave;p&agrave;dises&agrave;ya nibb&agrave;nadh&agrave;tuy&agrave;
parinibb&agrave;yati, na upeti sa&iuml;khanti: anup&agrave;dises&agrave;ya
nibb&agrave;nadh&agrave;tuy&agrave; parinibbuto sa&iuml;kha&uuml; na upeti
uddesa&uuml; na upeti ga&otilde;ana&uuml; na upeti, pa&otilde;&otilde;atti&uuml;
na upeti, khattiyoti v&agrave; br&agrave;hma&otilde;oti v&agrave; vessoti
v&agrave; suddoti v&agrave; gaha&ntilde;&ntilde;hoti v&agrave; pabbajitoti
v&agrave; devoti v&agrave; manussoti v&agrave; r&aring;p&atilde;ti v&agrave;
ar&aring;p&atilde;ti v&agrave; sa&curren;&curren;&atilde;ti v&agrave; asa&curren;&curren;&atilde;ti
v&agrave; nevasa&curren;&curren;&atilde;n&agrave;sa&curren;&curren;&atilde;ti
v&agrave; so hetu natthi, paccayo natthi, k&agrave;ra&otilde;a&uuml; natthi,
yena sa&iuml;kha&uuml; gaccheyy&agrave;ti 'attha&uuml; paleti na upeti
sa&iuml;kha&uuml;. '</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Ten&agrave;ha bhagav&agrave;:</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">''Acci yath&agrave; v&agrave;tavegena khitt&agrave;
(upas&atilde;v&agrave;ti bhagav&agrave;)</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Attha&uuml; paleti na upeti sa&iuml;kha&uuml;,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Eva&uuml; mun&atilde; n&agrave;mak&agrave;y&agrave;
vimutto</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Attha&uuml; paleti na upeti sa&iuml;khanti''.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">6-7</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Attha&uuml; gato so uda v&agrave; natthi</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Ud&agrave;hu ve sassatiy&agrave; arogo,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Ta&uuml; me mun&atilde; s&agrave;dhu viy&agrave;karohi</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Tath&agrave; hi te vidito esa dhammo.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Attha&uuml; gato so uda v&agrave; so natth&atilde;ti:
so attha&uuml; gato ud&agrave;hu natthi, so niruddho ucchinno vina&ntilde;&ntilde;hoti
'attha&uuml; gato so uda v&agrave; so natthi'.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Ud&agrave;hu vo sassatiy&agrave; arogoti 'ud&agrave;hu
nicco dhuvo sassato aviparin&agrave;madhammo sassatisama&uuml; tatheva
ti&ntilde;&ntilde;heyy&agrave;ti 'ud&agrave;hu ve sassatiy&agrave; arogo.
'</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Ta&uuml; me mun&atilde; s&agrave;dhu viy&agrave;karoh&atilde;ti
'ta'nti: ya&uuml; pucch&agrave;mi, ya&uuml; y&agrave;c&agrave;mi, ya&uuml;
ajjhes&agrave;mi, ya&uuml; pas&agrave;demi. Mun&atilde;ti 'mona&uuml;'
vuccati &curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml;, y&agrave; pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;
paj&agrave;nan&agrave; vicayo pavicayo dhammavicayo sallakkha&otilde;&agrave;
upalakkha&otilde;&agrave; paccupalakkha&otilde;&agrave; pa&otilde;&oacute;icca&uuml;
kosalla&uuml; nepu&curren;&curren;a&uuml; vebhavy&agrave; cint&agrave;
upaparikkh&agrave; bh&aring;ri medh&agrave; pari&otilde;&agrave;yik&agrave;
vipassan&agrave; sampaja&curren;&curren;a&uuml; patodo pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;
pa&curren;&curren;indriya&uuml; pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;bala&uuml; pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;sattha&uuml;
pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;p&agrave;s&agrave;do pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;&agrave;loko
pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;obh&agrave;so pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;pajjoto
pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;p&agrave;s&agrave;do pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;&agrave;loko
pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;obh&agrave;so pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;pajjoto
pa&curren;&curren;&agrave;ratana&uuml; amoho dhammavicayo samm&agrave;di&ntilde;&ntilde;hi,
tena &curren;&agrave;&otilde;ena samann&agrave;gato muni monappattoti.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">T&atilde;&otilde;i moneyy&agrave;ni: k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;
vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml; manomoneyya&uuml;. Katama&uuml; k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;?
Tividh&agrave;na&uuml; k&agrave;yaduccarit&agrave;na&uuml; pah&agrave;na&uuml;
k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;. Tividha&uuml; k&agrave;yasucarita&uuml; k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;,
k&agrave;y&agrave;ramma&otilde;e &curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml; k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;,
k&agrave;yapari&curren;&curren;&agrave; k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;, pari&curren;&curren;&agrave;sahagato
maggo k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;, k&agrave;ye chandar&agrave;gassa pah&agrave;na&uuml;
k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;, k&agrave;yasa&uuml;kh&agrave;r&agrave;nirodho
catutthajjh&agrave;nasam&agrave;patti k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;. Ida&uuml;
k&agrave;yamoneyya&uuml;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Katama&uuml; vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;? Catubbidh&agrave;na&uuml;
vac&atilde;duccarit&agrave;na&uuml; pah&agrave;na&uuml; vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;,
vac&atilde;sucarita&uuml; vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;, v&agrave;c&agrave;ramma&otilde;e
&curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml; vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;, v&agrave;c&agrave;pari&curren;&curren;&agrave;
vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;, pari&curren;&curren;&agrave;sahagato maggo vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;,
v&agrave;c&agrave;ya chandar&agrave;gassa pah&agrave;na&uuml; vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;.
Vac&atilde;sa&uuml;kh&agrave;ranirodho dutiyajjh&agrave;nasam&agrave;patti
vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;. Ida&uuml; vac&atilde;moneyya&uuml;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Katama&uuml; manomoneyya&uuml;? Tividh&agrave;na&uuml;
manoduccarit&agrave;na&uuml; pah&agrave;na&uuml; manomoneyya&uuml;, tividha&uuml;
manosucarita&uuml; manomoneyya&uuml;, citt&agrave;ramma&otilde;e &curren;&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml;
manomoneyya&uuml;, cittapari&curren;&curren;&agrave; manomoneyya&uuml;,
pari&curren;&curren;&agrave;sahagato maggo manomoneyya&uuml;, citte chandar&agrave;gassa
pah&agrave;na&uuml; manomoneyya&uuml;, cittasa&uuml;kh&agrave;ranirodho
sa&curren;&curren;&agrave;vedayitanirodhasam&agrave;patti manomoneyya&uuml;.
Ida&uuml; manomoneyya&uuml;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">1. ''K&agrave;yamuni&uuml; v&agrave;c&agrave;muni&uuml;
manomuniman&agrave;sava&uuml;,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Muni&uuml; moneyyasampanna&uuml; &agrave;hu
sabbappah&agrave;yina&uuml;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">2. K&agrave;yamuni&uuml; v&agrave;c&agrave;muni&uuml;
manomuniman&agrave;sava&uuml;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Muni&uuml; moneyyasampanna&uuml; &agrave;hu
ninh&agrave;tap&agrave;paka''nti.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Imehi t&atilde;hi moneyyehi dhammehi samann&agrave;gato
cha munino: ag&agrave;ramunino anag&agrave;ramunino sekhamunino asekhamunino
paccekamunino munimuninoti. Katame ag&agrave;ramunino? Ye te ag&agrave;rik&agrave;
di&ntilde;&ntilde;hapad&agrave; vi&curren;&curren;&agrave;tas&agrave;san&agrave;,
ime ag&agrave;ramunino. Katame anag&agrave;ramunino? Ye te pabbajit&agrave;
di&ntilde;&ntilde;hapad&agrave; vi&curren;&curren;&agrave;tas&agrave;san&agrave;,
ime anag&agrave;ramunino. Satta sekh&agrave; sekhamunino. Arahanto asekhamunino.
Paccekabuddh&agrave; paccekamunino. Munimunino vuccanti tath&agrave;gat&agrave;
arahanto samm&agrave;sambuddh&agrave;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">3. ''Na monena muni hoti m&aring;&euml;har&aring;po
aviddasu,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Yo ca tula&uuml;va paggayha varam&agrave;d&agrave;ya
pa&otilde;&oacute;ito.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">4. P&agrave;p&agrave;ni parivajjeti sa mun&atilde;
tena so mun&atilde;,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Yo mun&agrave;ti ubho loke mun&atilde; tena
pavuccat&atilde;. ''</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">5. ''Asata&curren;ca sata&curren;ca &curren;atv&agrave;
dhamma&uuml;</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Ajjhatta&uuml; bahiddh&agrave; ca sabbaloke,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Devamanussehi p&aring;jito yo</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Sa&iuml;gaj&agrave;lamaticca so mun&atilde;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">S&agrave;dhu viy&agrave;karoh&atilde;ti: s&agrave;dhu
&agrave;cikkh&agrave;hi desehi pa&curren;&curren;apehi pa&ntilde;&ntilde;hapehi
vivar&agrave;hi vibhaj&agrave;hi utt&agrave;n&atilde;karohi pak&agrave;seh&atilde;ti
'ta&uuml; me mun&atilde; s&agrave;dhu viy&agrave;karohi'.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">[BJT Page 238] [\x 238/]</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Tath&agrave; hi te vidito esa dhammoti: tath&agrave;
hi te vidito tulito t&atilde;rito vibh&aring;to vibh&agrave;vito esa dhammoti
'tath&agrave; hi te vidito esa dhammo'.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Ten&agrave;ha so br&agrave;hma&otilde;o:</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">''Attha&uuml; gato so uda v&agrave; so natthi</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Ud&agrave;hu ve sassatiy&agrave; arogo,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Ta&uuml; me mun&atilde; s&agrave;dhu viy&agrave;karohi</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Tath&agrave; hi te vidito esa dhammo''ti.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">6-8</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Attha&uuml; gatassa na pam&agrave;&otilde;amatthi
(upas&atilde;v&agrave;ti bhagav&agrave;)</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Yena na&uuml; vajju1 ta&uuml; tassa natthi,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Sabbesu dhammesu sam&aring;hatesu</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Sam&aring;hat&agrave; v&agrave;dapath&agrave;pi
sabbe.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Attha&uuml; gatassa na pam&agrave;&otilde;amatth&atilde;ti:
'attha&uuml; gatass&agrave;'ti anup&agrave;dises&agrave;ya nibb&agrave;nadh&agrave;tuy&agrave;
parinibbutassa r&aring;papam&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml; natthi, vedan&agrave;pam&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml;
natthi, sa&curren;&curren;&agrave;pam&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml; natthi, sa&uuml;kh&agrave;rapam&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml;
natthi, vi&curren;&curren;&agrave;&otilde;apam&agrave;&otilde;a&uuml; natthi.
Natthi na (santi) na sa&uuml;vijjati n&aring;palabbhati. Pah&atilde;na&uuml;
samucchinna&uuml; v&aring;pasanta&uuml; pa&ntilde;ippassaddha&uuml; abhabbuppattika&uuml;
&curren;&agrave;&otilde;aggin&agrave; da&oacute;&oacute;hanti 'attha&uuml;
gatassa na pam&agrave;&otilde;amatthi. Upas&atilde;v&agrave;ti bhagav&agrave;ti
'upas&atilde;v&agrave;'ti bhagav&agrave; ta&uuml; br&agrave;hma&otilde;a&uuml;
n&agrave;mena &agrave;lapati, bhagav&agrave;ti g&agrave;rav&agrave;dhivacanameta&uuml;:</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Apica, bhaggar&agrave;goti bhagav&agrave;:
bhaggadosoti bhagav&agrave;: bhaggamohoti bhagav&agrave;: bhaggam&agrave;noti
bhagav&agrave;: bhaggadi&ntilde;&ntilde;h&atilde;ti bhagav&agrave;: bhaggaka&otilde;&ntilde;akoti
bhagav&agrave;: bhaggakilesoti bhagav&agrave;: bhaji vibhaji pavibhaji
dhammaratananti bhagav&agrave;: bhav&agrave;na&uuml; antakaroti bhagav&agrave;
: bh&agrave;vitak&agrave;yo bh&agrave;vitas&atilde;lo bh&agrave;vitacitto
bh&agrave;vitapa&curren;&curren;oti bhagav&agrave;: bhaji v&agrave; bhagav&agrave;
ara&curren;&curren;e vanapatth&agrave;ni pant&agrave;ni sen&agrave;san&agrave;ni
appasadd&agrave;ni appanigghos&agrave;ni vijanav&agrave;t&agrave;ni manussar&agrave;haseyyak&agrave;ni
pa&ntilde;isall&agrave;nas&agrave;rupp&agrave;n&atilde;ti bhagav&agrave;:
bh&agrave;g&atilde; v&agrave; bhagav&agrave; c&atilde;varapi&otilde;&oacute;ap&agrave;tasen&agrave;sanagil&agrave;napaccayabhesajjaparikkh&agrave;r&agrave;nanti
bhagav&agrave;: bh&agrave;g&atilde; v&agrave; bhagav&agrave; attharasassa
dhammarasassa vimuttirasassa adhis&atilde;lassa adhicittassa adhipa&curren;&curren;&agrave;y&agrave;ti
bhagav&agrave;.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Bh&agrave;g&atilde; v&agrave; bhagav&agrave;
catunna&uuml; jh&agrave;n&agrave;na&uuml; catunna&uuml; appama&curren;&curren;&agrave;na&uuml;
catunna&uuml; ar&aring;pasam&agrave;patt&atilde;nanti bhagav&agrave;, bh&agrave;g&atilde;
v&agrave; bhagav&agrave; a&ntilde;&ntilde;hanna&uuml; vimokkh&agrave;na&uuml;
a&ntilde;&ntilde;hanna&uuml; abhibh&agrave;yatan&agrave;na&uuml; navanna&uuml;
anupubbavih&agrave;rasam&agrave;patt&atilde;nanti bhagav&agrave;: bh&agrave;g&atilde;
v&agrave; bhagav&agrave; dasanna&uuml; sa&curren;&curren;&agrave;bh&agrave;van&agrave;na&uuml;
dasanna&uuml; kasi&otilde;asam&agrave;patt&atilde;na&uuml;, &agrave;n&agrave;p&agrave;nasatisam&agrave;dhissa
asubhasam&agrave;pattiy&agrave;ti bhagav&agrave;, bh&agrave;g&atilde; v&agrave;
bhagav&agrave; catunna&uuml; satipa&ntilde;&ntilde;h&agrave;n&agrave;na&uuml;
catunna&uuml; sammappadh&agrave;n&agrave;na&uuml; catunna&uuml; iddhip&agrave;d&agrave;na&uuml;
pa&curren;canna&uuml; indriy&agrave;na&uuml; pa&curren;canna&uuml; bal&agrave;na&uuml;
sattanna&uuml; bojjha&iuml;g&agrave;na&uuml; ariyassa a&ntilde;&ntilde;ha&iuml;gikassa
maggass&agrave;ti bhagav&agrave;: bh&agrave;g&atilde; v&agrave; bhagav&agrave;
dasanna&uuml; tath&agrave;gatabal&agrave;na&uuml; catunna&uuml; ves&agrave;rajj&agrave;na&uuml;
catunna&uuml; pa&ntilde;isambhid&agrave;na&uuml; channa&uuml; abhi&curren;&curren;&agrave;na&uuml;
channa&uuml; buddhadhamm&agrave;nanti bhagav&agrave;: bhagav&agrave;ti
neta&uuml; n&agrave;ma&uuml; m&agrave;tar&agrave; kata&uuml;, na pitar&agrave;
kata&uuml;, na bh&agrave;tar&agrave; kata&uuml;, na bhaginiy&agrave; kata&uuml;,
na mitt&agrave;maccehi kata&uuml;, na &curren;&agrave;tis&agrave;lohitehi
kata&uuml;, na sama&otilde;abr&agrave;hma&otilde;ehi kata&uuml;, na devat&agrave;hi
kata&uuml;, vimokkhantikameta&uuml; buddh&agrave;na&uuml; bhagavant&agrave;na&uuml;
bodhiy&agrave; m&aring;le saha sabba&curren;&curren;uta&curren;&agrave;&otilde;assa
pa&ntilde;il&agrave;bh&agrave; sacchik&agrave; pa&curren;&curren;atti yadida&uuml;
bhagav&agrave;ti 'upas&atilde;v&agrave;ti bhagav&agrave;. '</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Yena na&uuml; vajju ta&uuml; tassa natth&atilde;ti:
yena r&agrave;gena vadeyyu&uuml;, yena dosena vadeyyu&uuml;, yena mohena
vadeyyu&uuml;, yena m&agrave;nena vadeyyu&uuml;, y&agrave;ya di&ntilde;&ntilde;hiy&agrave;
vadeyyu&uuml;, yena uddhaccena vadeyyu&uuml;, y&agrave;ya vicikicch&agrave;ya
vadeyyu&uuml;, yehi anusayehi vadeyyu&uuml;, rattoti v&agrave; du&ntilde;&ntilde;hoti
v&agrave; m&aring;&euml;hoti v&agrave; vinibaddhoti v&agrave; par&agrave;ma&ntilde;&ntilde;hoti
v&agrave; vikkhepagatoti v&agrave; ani&ntilde;&ntilde;ha&iuml;gatoti v&agrave;
th&agrave;magatoti v&agrave; te abhisa&iuml;kh&agrave;r&agrave; pah&atilde;n&agrave;,
abhisa&iuml;kh&agrave;r&agrave;na&uuml; pah&atilde;natt&agrave; gatiy&agrave;
yena vadeyyu&uuml; nerayikoti v&agrave; tiracch&agrave;nayonikoti v&agrave;
pettivisayikoti v&agrave; manussoti v&agrave; devoti v&agrave; r&aring;p&atilde;ti
v&agrave; ar&aring;p&atilde;ti v&agrave; sa&curren;&curren;&atilde;ti v&agrave;
asa&curren;&curren;&atilde;ti v&agrave; nevasa&curren;&curren;&atilde;n&agrave;sa&curren;&curren;&atilde;ti
v&agrave; so hetu natthi, paccayo natthi, k&agrave;ra&otilde;a&uuml; natthi,
yena vadeyyu&uuml; katheyyu&uuml; bha&otilde;eyyu&uuml; d&atilde;peyyu&uuml;
vohareyyunti 'yena na&uuml; vajju ta&uuml; tassa natthi. '</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">1. Vajju&uuml; - machasa&uuml;</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">[BJT Page 240] [\x 240/]</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Sabbesu dhammesu sam&aring;hates&aring;ti: sabbesu
dhammesu sabbesu khandhesu sabbesu &agrave;yatanesu sabbesu dh&agrave;tusu1
sabb&agrave;su gatisu sabb&agrave;su upapattisu sabb&agrave;su pa&ntilde;isandhisu
sabbesu bhavesu sabbesu sa&uuml;s&agrave;resu sabbesu va&ntilde;&ntilde;esu
&aring;hatesu sam&aring;hatesu uddhatesu samuddhatesu upp&agrave;&ntilde;itesu
samupp&agrave;&ntilde;itesu pah&atilde;nesu samucchinnesu v&aring;pasannesu
pa&ntilde;ippassaddhesu abhabbuppattikesu &curren;&agrave;&otilde;aggin&agrave;
da&oacute;&oacute;hes&aring;ti 'sabbesu dhammesu sam&aring;hatesu. '</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Sam&aring;hat&agrave; v&agrave;dapath&agrave;pi
sabbeti: 'v&agrave;dapath&agrave;' vuccanti kiles&agrave; ca khandh&agrave;
ca abhisa&uuml;kh&agrave;r&agrave; ca, tassa v&agrave;d&agrave; ca v&agrave;dapath&agrave;
ca adhivacan&agrave;ni ca adhivacanapath&agrave; ca nirutt&atilde; ca niruttipath&agrave;
ca pa&curren;&curren;att&atilde; ca pa&curren;&curren;attipath&agrave;
ca &aring;hat&agrave; sam&aring;hat&agrave; uddhat&agrave; samuddhat&agrave;
upp&agrave;&ntilde;it&agrave; samupp&agrave;&ntilde;it&agrave; pah&atilde;n&agrave;
samucchinn&agrave; v&aring;pasant&agrave; pa&ntilde;ippassaddh&agrave;
abhabbuppattik&agrave; &curren;&agrave;&otilde;aggin&agrave; da&oacute;&oacute;h&agrave;ti
'sam&aring;hat&agrave; v&agrave;dapath&agrave;pi sabbe. '</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Ten&agrave;ha bhagav&agrave;:</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">''Attha&uuml; gatassa na pam&agrave;&otilde;amatthi
(upas&atilde;v&agrave;ti bhagav&agrave;)</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Yena na&uuml; vajju ta&uuml; tassa natthi,</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Sabbesu dhammesu sam&aring;hatesu</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Sam&aring;hat&agrave; v&agrave;dapath&agrave;pi
sabbe''ti.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Saha g&agrave;th&agrave;pariyos&agrave;n&agrave;
ye te br&agrave;hma&otilde;ena saddhi&uuml; ekacchand&agrave; ekapayogo
ek&agrave;dhipp&agrave;y&agrave; ekav&agrave;sanav&agrave;sit&agrave;,
2 tesa&uuml; anekap&agrave;&otilde;asahass&agrave;na&uuml; viraja&uuml;
v&atilde;tamala&uuml; dhammacakkhu&uuml; udap&agrave;di. 'Ya&uuml; ki&curren;ci
samudayadhamma&uuml; sabba&uuml; ta&uuml; nirodhadhamma'nti. Tassa br&agrave;hma&otilde;assa
anup&agrave;d&agrave;ya &agrave;savehi citta&uuml; vimucci. Saha arahattappatt&agrave;
ajinaja&ntilde;&agrave;v&agrave;kac&atilde;ratida&otilde;&oacute;akama&otilde;&oacute;alu
kes&agrave; ca massu ca antarahit&agrave;. Bha&otilde;&oacute;u k&agrave;s&agrave;yavatthavasano
sa&iuml;gh&agrave;&ntilde;ipattac&atilde;varadharo anavatthapa&ntilde;ipattiy&agrave;
pa&curren;jaliko namassam&agrave;no nisinno</font>
<br><font face="Times_CSX+">Hoti: 'satth&agrave; me bhante bhagav&agrave;
s&agrave;vako' hama'sm&atilde;ti.</font><font face="Times_CSX+"></font>
<center>
<p><font face="Times_CSX+">Upas&atilde;vasuttaniddeso cha&ntilde;&ntilde;ho.</font></center>
